  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a pan, heat 1 tablespoon of oil over medium heat. Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the ginger, cumin powder, and coriander powder. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the chickpeas, salt, and fermented yogurt. Cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish.",
    "Top with the crumble mixture.",
